== Turkey Sausage & Cheese Egg Bites ==

Open @Turkey Sausage & Cheese Egg Bites{2} packaging slightly to vent. With egg bite in 
packaging, microwave until heated through, ~{40-60%seconds}.

Alternatively, preheat #toaster oven{} to 350 degrees. Remove egg bite from plastic 
packaging and toast in toaster oven until heated through, ~{5-10%minutes}.

== Breakfast Sausage ==

Heat a drizzle of @oil{drizzle} in a #large pan{} over medium-high heat. Add @Maple 
Pork Breakfast Sausage{1} and cook, turning occasionally, until browned all over 
and cooked through, ~{8-12%minutes}.

> Oven alternative: Preheat oven to 425 degrees. Place sausage on a #baking sheet{}. 
Roast until browned and cooked through, 18-20 minutes.

> Breakfast Sausage is fully cooked when internal temperature reaches 160°.

== Liege Waffles ==

Heat a #waffle iron{}. Add @Liege Waffle{4} to iron. Warm for about ~{30%seconds}.

Toaster or oven alternative: Heat #toaster{} or #traditional oven{} to low. Add 
waffle to toaster or oven. Warm for about ~{1%minute}.

Microwave alternative: Microwave waffle for ~{20%seconds}.

== Assembly ==

Arrange egg bites, breakfast sausage, waffles, and @Cinnamon Crumb Cake Muffin{2} on 
a #board{} or #platter{}. Garnish with @?fresh fruit{} or @?flowers{} and serve!

> We suggest doubling down on the maple by also serving warm syrup on the side. 
Couple this board with coffee for some extra wow factor.